Package signalGreen

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CarVehicle
    CarVehicle simulates vehicles of type Car.
    Constants
    Constant class holds all arbitrary calibration parameters derived from manual testing of Signal Green.
    CoordinateAgent
    Auxiliary agent just for setting auxiliary coordinates to be used as placeholders on the GIS projection.
    GisAgent
    A generic GIS agent.
    GiveWaySign
    Give Way sign junction for traffic management policies.
    Junction
    Generic class for junctions of the Traffic Simulator.
    A Junction object is a node on a Graph.
    LaneAgent
    Auxiliary agent used to display lanes on the GIS projection.
    Light
    Light object for Traffic Light Junctions.
    Road
    Road agent is used to display the road on the GIS display.
    SignalGreenBuilder
    This is custom context builder implementation which is responsible to perform the initialization of the Traffic Simulator.
    TrafficLight
    TrafficLight object is a subclass of the Junction object.
    TruckVehicle
    Trucks are the slowest vehicles in Signal Green.
    Utils
    Most utility functions are used for geographic calculations, such as distance between coordinates or azimuth of a road segment.
    Vehicle
    Generic class for vehicles of the Traffic Simulator.
    Cars, ambulances, trucks are subclasses of Vehicle, and have special behaviour such as cars having reckless or cautious drivers.
